---

<section
  class="pt-20 pb-20 bg-color-secondary rounded-t-[60px] border-t border-color box-shadow"
>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-8 lg:px-10">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-text mb-4">
          How Openlane Streamlines NIST 800-53 Compliance
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Open-source platform for managing federal information security
          controls and continuous monitoring
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- Control Implementation -->
        <div
          class="bg-card p-6 rounded-lg border border-border hover:border-primary transition-colors"
        >
          <div class="mb-4">
            <div
              class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-6 h-6 text-primary"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-2">
              Security Control Implementation
            </h4>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Implement and track all 20 control families across Low, Moderate,
            and High impact baselines. Map controls to your specific system
            categorization and authorization requirements.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span>
              <span>1,000+ control templates</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span>
              <span>Baseline selection (Low/Mod/High)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span>
              <span>Control tailoring workflows</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Risk Management -->
        <div
          class="bg-card p-6 rounded-lg border border-border hover:border-primary transition-colors"
        >
          <div class="mb-4">
            <div
              class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-6 h-6 text-primary"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-2">
              Risk Management Framework
            </h4>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Align with NIST RMF processes for system categorization, control
            selection, implementation, assessment, authorization, and continuous
            monitoring per NIST SP 800-37.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span>
              <span>FIPS 199 categorization</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span>
              <span>RMF step tracking</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span>
              <span>ATO package generation</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Continuous Monitoring -->
        <div
          class="bg-card p-6 rounded-lg border border-border hover:border-primary transition-colors"
        >
          <div class="mb-4">
            <div
              class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-6 h-6 text-primary"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M9 17v-2m3 2v-4m3 4v-6m2 10H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-2">
              Continuous Monitoring Program
            </h4>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Automate ongoing assessment of security controls, track control
            effectiveness, and maintain real-time security posture visibility
            required for continuous ATO.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span>
              <span>Automated control testing</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span>
              <span>Real-time status dashboards</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span>
              <span>Deviation tracking & remediation</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- System Security Plans -->
        <div
          class="bg-card p-6 rounded-lg border border-border hover:border-primary transition-colors"
        >
          <div class="mb-4">
            <div
              class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-6 h-6 text-primary"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-2">
              System Security Plan (SSP) Generation
            </h4>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Generate comprehensive SSPs documenting system boundaries, control
            implementation, and security measures. Export OSCAL-formatted
            documentation for federal submissions.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span>
              <span>SSP templates & automation</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span>
              <span>OSCAL format support</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span>
              <span>Version control & updates</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Assessment & Authorization -->
        <div
          class="bg-card p-6 rounded-lg border border-border hover:border-primary transition-colors"
        >
          <div class="mb-4">
            <div
              class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-6 h-6 text-primary"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-2">
              Assessment & Authorization Support
            </h4>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Prepare for security control assessments with organized evidence
            packages, assessment plans, POA&Ms, and comprehensive documentation
            for authorizing officials.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span>
              <span>SAP & SAR generation</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span>
              <span>POA&M tracking</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span>
              <span>Evidence collection automation</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Access Control & Audit -->
        <div
          class="bg-card p-6 rounded-lg border border-border hover:border-primary transition-colors"
        >
          <div class="mb-4">
            <div
              class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-6 h-6 text-primary"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-2">
              Access Control & Audit Logging
            </h4>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Implement AC and AU family controls with automated log collection,
            access reviews, least privilege enforcement, and comprehensive audit
            trails for federal systems.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span>
              <span>Centralized audit log management</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span>
              <span>Access control enforcement</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span>
              <span>Quarterly access reviews</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA Section -->
      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <div class="bg-card p-8 rounded-lg border border-border">
          <h4 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">
            Ready to Achieve NIST 800-53 Compliance?
          </h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Start your 30-day free trial and streamline federal security
            controls with Openlane's comprehensive RMF platform.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a
              href="/signup"
              class="px-6 py-3 bg-primary text-white font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors"
            >
              Start Free Trial
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
